  <brief_title>Comparison of the Guide-wire G-240 to a Combination of a Flexible/Hydrophil and a Nitinol Guide Wire</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of the Use of the Guide-wire G-240 to a Combination of a Flexible/Hydrophil Guide Wire With a Nitinol Wire in Patients With Stenosis of the Bile Ducts in ERCP</official_title>
  <sponsors>
